description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'BEST Exercises for Runners (Strength Training | Plyometrics | Power Exercises)' from the channel E3 Rehab.
The workout falls under Cardio/Running and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Other and Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Athlete's Circuit and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
